title: NutriChef 26L Electric Air Fryer Oven | 1700W Countertop Rotisserie & Air Fryer | 360° Rotating Feature | 10 Digital Menu Presets | Includes Drip Tray, Air Frying Basket & Bake Rack 15x16x14 (Silver)
description: Introducing the 26L Electric Air Fryer Oven, a sleek and powerful kitchen essential that brings versatility to your cooking routine. With 1700 watts of heating element, this countertop rotisserie combo offers 10 digital quick menu presets, including Air Fry, Toast, Bake, Broil, Roast, Reheat, Warm, Slow Cook, and Dehydrate. Its non-stick, easy-to-clean design and adjustable temperature control (up to 400°F) provide precise cooking, while the automatic shut-off and overheat protection prioritize safety. The 360° hot air circulation technology ensures quick and even cooking with minimal oil, and the compact size allows for easy storage. Equipped with a high-definition LED touch screen and transparent window, this air fryer oven delivers a seamless cooking experience. Complete with a dishwasher-safe tray and a comprehensive accessory package, it's the perfect appliance for those seeking a healthier and more efficient cooking solution. Elevate your kitchen with the 26L Electric Air Fryer Oven – where innovation meets culinary excellence.
